OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1771882264
OL,3,CCCTV shows 'violent' knife-wielding
OL,4,Cman launch attack in shop
OL,6,FA knife-wielding man has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor three years after attacking a man
OL,8,Fat a shop in Kent.
OL,10,FMichael Tucker was seen on CCTV
OL,11,Fbrandishing the weapon when he saw a
OL,12,Fman he held a grudge against, at a
OL,13,Fstore in Ordnance Street, Chatham, on
OL,14,F19 August 2025.
OL,16,FThe victim, who had tried to defend
OL,17,Fhimself, was left with a deep cut to
OL,18,Fhis hand during the confrontation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
