FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1771882264
OL,3,CCCTV shows 'violent' knife-wielding
OL,4,Cman launch attack in shop
OL,6,FTucker was arrested the following day
OL,7,Fand charged with attempting to cause
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm, assault, and
OL,9,Fthreatening a person with an offensive
OL,10,Fweapon.
OL,12,FThe 59-year-old, of Fort Pitt Street,
OL,13,FChatham, admitted to all three charges
OL,14,Fand was jailed for 37 months at
OL,15,FMaidstone Crown Court on Monday 16
OL,16,FFebruary 2026.
OL,18,FA restraining order was also imposed
OL,19,Ffor five years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
