FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1771882264
OL,3,CCCTV shows 'violent' knife-wielding
OL,4,Cman launch attack in shop
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Det Sgt Emily
OL,7,FMatthews said: "Michael Tucker has
OL,8,Fshown himself to be a violent person
OL,9,Fwho shows no concern in attacking
OL,10,Fpeople spontaneously and in a public
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,F"The victim could have suffered even
OL,14,Fworse injuries had he not been able to
OL,15,Fdefend himself. The community is safer
OL,16,Fnow that Tucker is behind bars."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
